Class ClassWrapper

java.lang.Object
  com.googlecode.transloader.ClassWrapper

public final class ClassWrapper
extends Object

The wrapper appropriate for wrapping around all Classes from potentially foreign ClassLoaders.

Author:
Jeremy Wales

isAssignableTo

public boolean isAssignableTo(String typeName)
Indicates whether or not the wrapped Class is assignable to a Class with the given name. It takes a parameter of type String instead of Class so that the test can be performed for Classes that do not have an equivalent in the caller's ClassLoader.

Parameters:
typeName - the name of the type to check against
Returns:
true if the wrapped Class is assignable to a Class with the given name
